label: 375. Receipt of monies received by Susan S. Keith from James B. Heyward -- 1840(?) -1873
description: Receipt of monies received by Susan S. Keith from James B. Heyward as executor/trustee of the estate of Nathaniel Heyward.  The receipts mostly depict interest from a bond bequeathed to Susan Keith in the will of Nathaniel Heyward.  30p.
